Title: 029: Dive Into Deep Learning and Find Out Where Machines Can Outperform Humans With Ben Taylor
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Chief Data Scientist Ben Taylor. You will learn about the role of AI in recruitment, know about a crash course in deep learning and discuss on where machines can outperform humans.
